418
00:24:48,269 --> 00:24:50,794
OK. We'll do it your way.

419
00:25:19,734 --> 00:25:21,224
What?

420
00:25:22,436 --> 00:25:24,267
I didn't say
you can come in here.

421
00:25:24,338 --> 00:25:25,703
I didn't ask. Man.

422
00:25:39,053 --> 00:25:40,577
So. What's your secret. Bro?

423
00:25:40,655 --> 00:25:43,453
