bring the pootie tang?

424
00:25:43,524 --> 00:25:44,923
What's that mean?

425
00:25:46,761 --> 00:25:49,161
You got yourself a lady friend
these days?

426
00:25:49,230 --> 00:25:50,424
None of your business.

427
00:25:50,498 --> 00:25:52,762
Hmm. You pokin' her?

428
00:25:52,833 --> 00:25:54,095
I'm eleven.

429
00:25:54,168 --> 00:25:56,864
Who cares. Man?
Tell me you've at least...

430
00:25:56,938 --> 00:25:58,838
slapped the old Gromberg
lip-lock on her.

431
00:25:58,906 --> 00:26:01,374
Not yet. But I'm gonna.

432
00:26:01,442 --> 00:26:03,603
That's all right. Man.
Come here.

433
00:26:03,678 --> 00:26:07,739
How many girls
have you macked so far?

434
00:26:07,815 --> 00:26:09,749
- None.
- None?

435
00:26:11,586 --> 00:26:12,917
None?

436
00:26:14,121 --> 00:26:16,282
Now. What's this
supposed to be?

437
00:26:16,357 --> 00:26:18,917
It's whatever you think it is.

438
00:26:18,993 --> 00:26:20,893
What does it look like to you?

439
00:26:20,962 --> 00:26:22,520
Like a piece of shit.

440
00:26:22,597 --> 00:26:25,566
Mitchell! He's just being
provocative. You know him.

441
00:26:25,633 --> 00:26:27,430
