451
00:26:56,631 --> 00:26:59,293
That's not fair. He's been
through a lot this past year.

452
00:26:59,367 --> 00:27:00,664
This year isn't any different
than any other year.

453
00:27:00,735 --> 00:27:03,226
He's still a ballbuster.
Except this year...

454
00:27:03,304 --> 00:27:06,068
