459
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,781
Well. He sure has
a funny way of showing it.

460
00:27:15,850 --> 00:27:18,614
Alex. He's not gonna be
around forever.

461
00:27:18,686 --> 00:27:22,486
Found it!
Wow. A thousand dollars.

462
00:27:22,556 --> 00:27:23,682
What?

463
00:27:24,892 --> 00:27:26,519
One for me and one for Asher.

464
00:27:26,594 --> 00:27:29,290
Wow!
Aren't you the lucky boy?

465
00:27:29,363 --> 00:27:33,299
Thank Granny and Pappy for
being so unbelievably generous.

466
00:27:33,367 --> 00:27:35,699
- Thanks. Granny.
- You're welcome. Honey.

467
00:27:39,473 --> 00:27:43,375
Hey. My boy. My boy.

468
00:27:52,186 --> 00:27:54,654
I wish you and Alex would stop.

469
00:27:54,722 --> 00:27:58,180
What? Jeez.

470
00:28:03,130 --> 00:28:04,620
