757
00:48:45,505 --> 00:48:46,802
Now's your chance.
And I've had...

758
00:48:46,873 --> 00:48:49,501
a little bit of experience.
You know?

759
00:48:49,575 --> 00:48:51,099
No. I'm good.

760
00:48:57,984 --> 00:49:01,977
Charge!

761
00:49:34,253 --> 00:49:36,414
I was thinking a nightgown...

762
