pitcher in the third inning.

775
00:50:41,421 --> 00:50:45,653
That was a big mistake...
a big mistake.

776
00:50:48,061 --> 00:50:50,552
Your bath is ready!

777
00:50:52,665 --> 00:50:54,929
And I'm ready. Too.

778
00:50:58,971 --> 00:51:03,374
Hey. Hey. You can't take a bath
in your clothes.

779
00:51:03,443 --> 00:51:04,808
Get up.

780
