876
00:58:13,511 --> 00:58:15,911
Fish don't like that.

877
00:58:24,122 --> 00:58:27,558
I got a call from Jim Lindsay
the other day. Dad.

878
00:58:27,625 --> 00:58:29,923
What's he calling you about?

879
00:58:29,994 --> 00:58:32,019
He said he saw
a guy out here...

880
00:58:32,096 --> 00:58:36,795
