on your instructions.

881
00:58:36,868 --> 00:58:40,201
So? Testing the market.

882
00:58:40,271 --> 00:58:42,535
- Testing the market?
- Yeah.

883
00:58:42,607 --> 00:58:44,973
Does that mean you're
trying to sell the house?

884
00:58:45,043 --> 00:58:46,135
Why do you care?

885
00:58:46,211 --> 00:58:49,078
What do you mean?
I love this house.

886
00:58:49,147 --> 00:58:50,705
It's got mom's memories
all over there.

887
00:58:50,782 --> 00:58:51,749
Why the hell would you
even think about...

888
00:58:51,816 --> 00:58:54,011
You never even
come up here anymore.

889
00:58:54,085 --> 00:58:56,519
We used to come here
all the time. And we will again.

890
00:58:56,588 --> 00:58:59,182
Why wouldn't you have
the decency to tell me?

891
00:58:59,257 --> 00:59:00,519
Maybe Rebecca and I...

892
00:59:00,592 --> 00:59:02,719
would like to take over
ownership of the property.

893
00:59:02,794 --> 00:59:04,421
I'm not asking you
to give it to me. Dad.

894
00:59:04,496 --> 00:59:06,828
God forbid.
We'd write you a check.

895
00:59:06,898 --> 00:59:11,995
Hey. Dad. Could you chill out?
You're scaring my bites.

896
00:59:12,070 --> 00:59:16,006
Asher. Don't hold
the pole like that.

897
00:59:16,074 --> 00:59:18,838
