the "moby Dick" crap. All right?

898
00:59:18,910 --> 00:59:20,775
Just leave Asher
out of this whole thing.

899
00:59:20,845 --> 00:59:21,812
Dad. I don't need your help.

900
00:59:21,880 --> 00:59:23,347
I'm not gonna have you
bringing Asher...

901
00:59:23,414 --> 00:59:25,405
into what happened to me
when I was growing up. Dad.

902
00:59:25,483 --> 00:59:28,384
- Is that so?
- That's so. Dad. Enough. OK?

903
00:59:28,453 --> 00:59:31,581
Your wife died.
I've lost my mother.

904
00:59:31,656 --> 00:59:35,353
That's enough. OK?
Just... enough.

905
00:59:35,426 --> 00:59:38,259
OK. Everybody. Group hug.
Come on.

906
00:59:38,329 --> 00:59:41,321
Don't be a smart ass. OK?
I wasn't talking to you.

907
00:59:41,399 --> 00:59:44,197
Stop trying to make everybody
cry with you all the time.

908
00:59:44,269 --> 00:59:46,100
I'm sick of that.

909
00:59:46,170 --> 00:59:49,037
Some men cry inside.

910
00:59:49,107 --> 00:59:50,540
That's what I'm saying. Pappy.

911
00:59:50,608 --> 00:59:52,940
Not everybody's a soggy
cracker like you. Dad.

912
00:59:53,011 --> 00:59:56,208
Holy shit! I got a fish. Man!

913
00:59:56,281 --> 00:59:57,612
Good going. He got it.

914
01:00:00,718 --> 01:00:02,117
Look at that thing!

915
01:00:04,289 --> 01:00:05,347
