916
01:00:05,423 --> 01:00:07,357
I know. It's a big one.
Oh. Shit.

917
01:00:07,425 --> 01:00:10,087
- The net.
- Where's the net?

918
01:00:10,161 --> 01:00:12,356
- Hurry up. Dad!
- Get it up!

919
01:00:12,430 --> 01:00:15,729
- Use your hands!
- I got it!

920
01:00:15,800 --> 01:00:18,667
I've got him.
I've got him. OK?

921
01:00:18,736 --> 01:00:20,795
OK. Here we go. All right.

922
01:00:20,872 --> 01:00:24,808
What the hell you doing. Man?
Damn! Tell me you didn't just...

923
01:00:24,876 --> 01:00:26,434
Schmuck!

924
01:00:26,511 --> 01:00:29,139
- What the hell?
- You had it in your hand!

925
01:00:29,213 --> 01:00:33,445
I'm sorry. OK?

926
01:00:35,253 --> 01:00:36,720
I'm sorry!

927
01:00:38,590 --> 01:00:43,425
Let's see if we can get
another one. Schmuck.

928
01:00:53,304 --> 01:00:54,999
Mean brisket. Mom.

929
01:00:55,073 --> 01:00:57,098
I had nothing to do with it.

930
01:00:57,175 --> 01:00:59,769
What's Pappy doing?
Can you see him?

931
01:00:59,844 --> 01:01:02,813
Watching TV.

932
01:01:02,880 --> 01:01:06,247
How can you just sit there?

933
01:01:06,317 --> 01:01:08,080
Go get him.

934
01:01:19,931 --> 01:01:22,923
- Dad...
- Not hungry.

935
01:01:31,309 --> 01:01:38,078
I'm sorry about the fish
and everything.

936
01:01:38,149 --> 01:01:42,108
If you change your mind.
We'd love you to join us.

937
01:01:49,961 --> 01:01:51,952
I finally get it
all the way into the boat...

938
01:01:52,030 --> 01:01:55,989
and what does my father do?
He drops the slippery sucker.

939
01:01:56,067 --> 01:01:59,503
Are you upset
about your grandmother?

940
01:01:59,570 --> 01:02:03,267
- Asher?
- Yeah. I'm here.

941
01:02:03,341 --> 01:02:05,809
You want to talk about it?

942
01:02:05,877 --> 01:02:09,040
No. Not particularly.

943
01:02:09,113 --> 01:02:11,877
I'm really sorry.

944
01:02:11,949 --> 01:02:14,008
Yeah. I know.

945
01:02:14,085 --> 01:02:18,146
