leFT for you.

988
01:04:23,247 --> 01:04:25,215
Oh. Jesus.

989
01:04:25,283 --> 01:04:29,720
- I tried to wait. I really did.
- Oh. My God. Oh. Jesus. No.

990
01:04:29,787 --> 01:04:32,119
I loved your mother very much.
And I know you did. Too...

991
01:04:32,190 --> 01:04:33,953
