would understand...

992
01:04:34,025 --> 01:04:36,152
that I couldn't go through
the motions any longer.

993
01:04:36,227 --> 01:04:38,491
- Honey. I know this looks bad...
- Bad?

994
01:04:38,563 --> 01:04:40,554
But it is not what you think.

995
01:04:40,631 --> 01:04:41,825
Oh. Bad!

996
01:04:41,899 --> 01:04:44,925
I have been acting like a crazy
person for the last two days...

997
01:04:45,002 --> 01:04:47,095
carrying around
another woman's panties...

998
01:04:47,171 --> 01:04:49,162
