Are you?

1586
01:45:10,359 --> 01:45:12,384
Don't worry.

1587
01:45:12,461 --> 01:45:18,627
The doctor says I've only got
a few good years.

1588
01:45:18,700 --> 01:45:20,429
Don't worry.

1589
