Just how much I miss you

1591
01:45:39,688 --> 01:45:41,781
You'll never know

1592
01:45:41,857 --> 01:45:47,727
Just how much I care

1593
01:45:51,233 --> 01:45:54,225
And if I tried

1594
01:45:54,303 --> 01:45:57,272
I still couldn't hide

1595
01:45:57,339 --> 01:46:00,604
