1596
01:46:04,046 --> 01:46:06,412
You ought to know

1597
01:46:06,481 --> 01:46:11,976
For haven't I told you so

1598
01:46:12,054 --> 01:46:15,854
A million or more times

1599
01:46:15,924 --> 01:46:19,291
You went away

1600
01:46:19,361 --> 01:46:23,991
